Name: huc12
Description: 12-digit code for the HUC12 watershed

Name: huc12name
Description: Name of HUC 12 watershed. If there's no name, defaults to the 12-digit code.

Name: restoregoal_ha
Description: Additional habitat hectares to restore so that there's enough food (i.e. energy) to support long-term average NAWMP population objectives.

Name: restoregoal_80th_ha
Description: Additional habitat hectares to restore so that there's enough food (i.e. energy) to support long-term average NAWMP population objectives.

Name: protectgoal_ha
Description: Habitat hectares to protect so that the long-term average NAWMP population goal energy requirements are protected.

Name: protectgoal_80th_ha
Description: The 80th percentile of habitat hectares to protect so that ï¿½

Name: available_ha
Description: Total amount of available habitat hectares, excluding built or impervious area, and existing habitat.

Name: protected_ha
Description: Total acres protected as easements or preserves in the watershed.

Name: protectedhabitat_ha
Description: Total acres of dabbling duck habitat protected in the watershed.

Name: huc12_ha
Description: Total hectares in the watershed.

Name: urban_ha
Description: Total urban hectares in the watershed.

Name: tothabitat_ha
Description: Total habitat hectares in the watershed.

Name: tothabitat_kcal
Description: Total energy (kcal) in all habitat types within the watershed.(Energy Supply / Availability)

Name: protected_kcal
Description: Total kilocalories of energy protected by fee and easements as of December 2020?

Name: lta_demand_kcal

Name: surpdef_kcal
Alias: Long-Term Average Energy Surplus or Deficit (kcal)

Name: lta_nrgprotrq_kcal
Description: Total energy demand minus total protected energy in the watershed.

Name: nrgprotrq_80th_kcal
Description: The 80th Percentile of total energy demand minus total protected energy.

Name: wtMean_kcal_per_ha
Description: Weighted average kcal/ha for all habitats in the watershed
